**File:** `/home/armel/Projects/OSS/bmad-module-skill-forge/src/shared/scripts/skf-severity-classify.py`, lines 56–63
**Confidence: 88**

The HIGH rule check for added exports is:

```python
for rule in HIGH_RULES:
    if f_type == rule["type"]:
        if f_category in rule["categories"]:
            if "threshold" in rule:
                if f_type == "added" and f_category == "export" and added_export_count &gt; rule["threshold"]:
                    return "HIGH"
            else:
                return "HIGH"
```

